.IX Subsection "new()"
.Vb 8
\&    my $link = WWW::Mechanize::Link\->new( {
\&        url  => $url,
\&        text => $text,
\&        name => $name,
\&        tag  => $tag,
\&        base => $base,
\&        attr => $attr_href,
\&    } );
.Ve
.PP
For compatibility, this older interface is also supported:
.PP
.Vb 1
\& new( $url, $text, $name, $tag, $base, $attr_href )
